{"tid":1691678,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"8種唔同嘅香城online玩家","createTime":"2019-11-03T18:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T20:15:06.000Z","uid":320676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4b1c77612549cd67eb72edb70eaf7f9bcf5d81","tid":1691678,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:11:53.000Z","msg":"4個月前香城上線，呢4個月我觀察到有好多唔同玩家嘅出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.絕對嘅前線</span></span><br />\n呢班人士氣係最高昂，佢哋出嚟嘅目的係殺恐怖分子同埋佔領敵方據點，所以會係最後先退嘅一班人。但同時士氣都最容易受波動，當見到大隊鳩退，佢哋士氣都會即刻降到最低，同時佢哋企最前，所以最易畀恐怖分子綁架做戰俘<br />\n代表：71政總，721西環上環嘅前線，727元朗，85七區開花，811尖沙咀，824觀塘，101荃灣，屯門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jS4tTso.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjS4tTso.gif&h=ff087ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.保守嘅前線</span></span><br />\n士氣較低嘅一班人，佢哋行動往往都做最壞打算。情況佔優時，會慢慢向前進攻，但咁樣做亦浪費好多時間，令恐怖分子有足夠時間增援，而且易受後排影響，危及最前線嘅玩家安全<br />\n代表：721上環，101沙燕橋，1020油尖旺，1027旺角<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.cosplayer</span></span><br />\n呢批人會令全部玩家大幅降低士氣，一定要改善<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBOyj83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBOyj83.jpg&h=8197e0bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4.無懼嘅街坊</span></span><br />\n呢班人好撚勁，會夠膽反擊恐怖分子，士氣永遠保持最高<br />\n代表：旺角，730葵涌，78月嘅黃大仙深水埗，屯門，沙田，元朗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OGwgd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OGwgd5.jpg&h=e980fbe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">5.屌狗嘅街坊</span></span><br />\n佢哋一樣係唔會退嘅人，但唔將武力反抗當做一種反抗方法，主要喺有錢區多<br />\n代表：太古，黃埔，馬鞍山，藍灣半島，麗晶花園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TS4awOa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTS4awOa.jpg&h=50d31d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.和理非</span></span><br />\n和平，唔理性，非暴力。一樣會進行屌狗行為，但同街坊比，一退後就唔會返嚟。呢批人嘅士氣極差，亦拖累成條team嘅士氣變差，必須即刻解決呢個問題<br />\n出現地點：除街坊戰之外都會出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">7.有決心嘅無裝者</span></span><br />\n雖然呢批人外表同和理非一樣，但佢哋係有返一定嘅決心同戰力，亦係最難估到嘅一批人，畀個口罩、手套同埋武器佢哋就有機會做出估你唔到嘅事<br />\n代表：612包圍 71政總 714新城市 1027尖沙咀 岳義士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">8.遊擊隊</span></span><br />\n佢哋士氣都麻麻，對大隊係失去信心。但每次攻擊都出其不意，如果可以配合大隊行動就更好，大隊又配合到佢哋就更好<br />\n代表：將軍澳單車空襲，825荃灣二坡坊，葵涌斬恐怖分子，割頸勇士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特殊進化方向<br />\n以上8種香城玩家遇到突發情況，會有機會出現「進化」，但呢個buff好短暫，下星期又會無咗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1.死線進化系</span></span><br />\n死線逼近，<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖分子唔投降</span>，香城玩家被責任感/情緒驅動，決定要進化，佢哋嘅攻擊力同防禦力都會提升，體力會短暫咁變得無窮無盡，會有決心咁向恐怖分子攻擊，唔理咩嘢放題都衝<br />\n代表：612包圍，71政總，721西環<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nEtY1E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nEtY1E.gif&h=05ad12b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ukcfD1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FukcfD1F.jpg&h=740c56af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2.絕地反擊系</span></span><br />\n香城玩家<span style=\"color: red;\">被恐怖分子威脅生命</span>，咁樣就觸發佢哋嘅求生本能，為咗生存會用盡全力掙扎反抗，大大力反咬恐怖分子，短時間內全部數值升到最高<br />\n代表：714新城市絕地大反擊，1027尖沙咀反擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxv8Y22.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxv8Y22.gif&h=435249e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">進化失敗嘅下場</span><br />\n第3、6種玩家經常進化失敗，而進化失敗嘅玩家會做出錯誤行為，令自己受更重嘅傷甚至死<br />\n例子：721元朗 831太子 <br />\n<br />\n例如跪地求饒，令恐怖分子更容易爆玩家頭，玩家亦更難逃走，並且做唔到防禦動作<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nuUUGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nuUUGY.jpg&h=94790442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中玩家更雙手合實，放棄最後嘅出拳機會，徹底令自己攻擊力同防禦力變做0<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cC05gWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcC05gWx.jpg&h=b2ec8b86&s={SIZE}\" />呢幾位玩家都作出錯誤嘅決定，將背脊露畀恐怖分子，喺戰場上放低武器同露出背後都係致死嘅行為，佢哋同樣犯咗721玩家嘅錯，跪低，不過有用雙手擋住恐怖分子噴劑攻擊，令佢哋不致於受重傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpT23F2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpT23F2.jpg&h=b929e6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下跪係示弱嘅行為，恐怖分子見到玩家下跪會好開心。恐怖分子覺得玩家廢，會打得仲狠"},{"pid":"190c9abb6a0b4a19aea317b641be4b93ee362cee","tid":1691678,"uid":117811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f88dffd3b100368e6baae57625f5aa0ae6125d","tid":1691678,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:17:18.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de6c79aa87c0fb1f29057a732500a2ac0eece09f","tid":1691678,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"好詳細"},{"pid":"51404449b0d0d21174b67333da58e1a7d104a958","tid":1691678,"uid":21986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e07ec2b0d99658c3070bb5008d8434875e24d14","tid":1691678,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8c5c184375237cee845290a1f9665a310b2b23","tid":1691678,"uid":8809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5904cee4fb4fa42e58b81321c7ce5cf176248d56","tid":1691678,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"P牌自推十連"},{"pid":"9066b7e9f64c723ec86ceb6d40ce2ca641278ad4","tid":1691678,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"17c6bb4a875b552c2b57002cddfd345c7c9ec143","tid":1691678,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3514be5e58a4f5898fd92d9a5e5c6d2736112f26","tid":1691678,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"30b40ab0326d8e8403858c2f5155cb8df0e6424c","tid":1691678,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T20:15:06.000Z","msg":"建議樓主重開po"}]}